CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 11, 1969, pg. 18 reads: "To Model in 'Fashion '69' - Fetching Fall Fashions will be modeled by these three attractive models along with a bevy of others. One lone male will also star in Gloria Grate's "Fashion '69" set for Sunday, Oct. 26, at 2:30 p.m. at Fort Duquesne Post 755, American Legion, 407 Devilliers St. Dinner plus the music of Bobby Jones is on program with Verneita Winston as commentator. - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Woman modeling poncho with arms raised and standing in hallway of Wesley Center A.M.E. Zion Church
